00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda svaki put

772
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad vidiš

773
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer poznaješ svoje djete,

774
00:26:49,059 --> 00:26:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] već ja znam i to djete

775
00:26:50,099 --> 00:26:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] i su tu djecu,

776
00:26:51,579 --> 00:26:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno primit ga,

777
00:26:52,359 --> 00:26:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] ne udaramo

778
00:26:53,359 --> 00:26:55,740
[SPEAKER_00] ili kad se dogodi opet

779
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] to udaranje,

780
00:26:56,900 --> 00:26:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] što u toj situaciji

781
00:26:58,380 --> 00:26:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] kad djete je,

782
00:26:58,900 --> 00:26:59,799
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći agresivno?

783
00:26:59,799 --> 00:27:00,759
[SPEAKER_01] Kad imamo djete

784
00:27:00,759 --> 00:27:02,160
[SPEAKER_01] koje je u fazi udaranja,

785
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] onda je zadača

786
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,339
[SPEAKER_01] nas roditelja

787
00:27:04,339 --> 00:27:05,200
[SPEAKER_01] ne da sjedimo

788
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] i pijemo kavu

789
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:06,799
[SPEAKER_01] i kažnjavamo ga

790
00:27:06,799 --> 00:27:07,759
[SPEAKER_01] jer udara tamo,

791
00:27:07,759 --> 00:27:09,180
[SPEAKER_01] nego idemo za njim.

792
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

793
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:10,900
[SPEAKER_01] činimo njega

794
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] sigurnim i okolinu.

795
00:27:12,619 --> 00:27:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] to je faza koja će stati,

796
00:27:15,079 --> 00:27:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] ali u toj fazi

797
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] mi moramo biti blizu.

798
00:27:17,539 --> 00:27:18,720
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ok,

799
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,440
[SPEAKER_01] ako to nije ne znam

800
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] kakav udarac,

801
00:27:20,059 --> 00:27:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] u redu je da nisi uvijek blizu,

802
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:22,799
[SPEAKER_01] ali generalno ovo,

803
00:27:22,799 --> 00:27:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] reci o prosti,

804
00:27:23,559 --> 00:27:25,799
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo se izignorira,

805
00:27:25,799 --> 00:27:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno ne napravi

806
00:27:26,559 --> 00:27:28,240
[SPEAKER_01] cijeli taj pozadinski dio.

807
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

808
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] njegovo udaranje

809
00:27:29,859 --> 00:27:31,480
[SPEAKER_01] je vrh sante leda.

810
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] I kad ti kažeš

811
00:27:32,859 --> 00:27:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] to se ne radi,

812
00:27:34,079 --> 00:27:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] reci o prosti,

813
00:27:35,180 --> 00:27:36,859
[SPEAKER_01] mi nismo dotakli

814
00:27:36,859 --> 00:27:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] ispod sante leda.

815
00:27:38,079 --> 00:27:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da bi djete

816
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] prestalo udarati,

817
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:40,240
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

818
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] ono će prestati udarati

819
00:27:41,359 --> 00:27:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] tako i ti njega kazniš

820
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] i udariš,

821
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:44,059
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda zbog boli

822
00:27:44,059 --> 00:27:45,160
[SPEAKER_01] će prestati udarati.

823
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ali,

824
00:27:46,259 --> 00:27:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

825
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] moramo se,

826
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,200
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se djete,

827
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:51,180
[SPEAKER_01] da bi razvilo

828
00:27:51,180 --> 00:27:52,759
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo svijesto sebi

829
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:54,019
[SPEAKER_01] i moglo u životu

830
00:27:54,019 --> 00:27:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] i u djetinstvu

831
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:55,940
[SPEAKER_01] kontrolirati sebe,

832
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:57,440
[SPEAKER_01] regulirati sebe

833
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,160
[SPEAKER_01] i da bi bilo uspješnije,

834
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] mi moramo se baviti

835
00:28:00,119 --> 00:28:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] ispod sante leda,

836
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:01,680
[SPEAKER_01] a to je

837
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] zašto on udara.

838
00:28:03,119 --> 00:28:04,339
[SPEAKER_01] I ti si sama

839
00:28:04,339 --> 00:28:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] dala nekakav hint

840
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] da bi to moglo biti

841
00:28:06,460 --> 00:28:07,240
[SPEAKER_01] i uzbuđen.

842
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:08,740
[SPEAKER_01] I jako lako moguće.

843
00:28:08,740 --> 00:28:09,819
[SPEAKER_01] I zapravo,

844
00:28:09,819 --> 00:28:10,779
[SPEAKER_01] ono što njemu

845
00:28:11,359 --> 00:28:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] ostaje.

846
00:28:11,579 --> 00:28:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] Da mu se kaže,

847
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:13,680
[SPEAKER_01] ne dozvoljavam da udaraš,

848
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,299
[SPEAKER_01] da ostavi se.

849
00:28:14,299 --> 00:28:15,819
[SPEAKER_01] I istog trena,

850
00:28:15,819 --> 00:28:17,460
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ima godina?

851
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:18,259
[SPEAKER_01] Cisla da tom,

852
00:28:18,259 --> 00:28:18,900
[SPEAKER_01] tri lagodin.

853
00:28:18,900 --> 00:28:19,220
[SPEAKER_01] Tri,

854
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:20,819
[SPEAKER_01] a moji su

855
00:28:20,819 --> 00:28:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] četiri.

856
00:28:21,759 --> 00:28:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] Uzbuđen si,

857
00:28:23,599 --> 00:28:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] čini se da si

858
00:28:24,619 --> 00:28:25,640
[SPEAKER_01] jako uzbuđen.

859
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] I ja mu,

860
00:28:26,119 --> 00:28:26,640
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

861
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] njemu se to u tijelu dogodi,

862
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:30,299
[SPEAKER_01] ali on ne zna što se dogodi.

863
00:28:30,299 --> 00:28:31,819
[SPEAKER_01] Njemu samo ide impuls.

864
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:33,819
[SPEAKER_01] A uloga nas,

865
00:28:33,819 --> 00:28:34,519
[SPEAKER_01] roditelja,

866
00:28:34,519 --> 00:28:35,940
[SPEAKER_01] odgajatelja,

867
00:28:35,940 --> 00:28:36,640
[SPEAKER_01] učitelja,

868
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,440
[SPEAKER_01] je da zapravo

869
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:39,279
[SPEAKER_01] pomognemo djeci

870
00:28:39,279 --> 00:28:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] da usvijeste šta je ispod.

871
00:28:40,599 --> 00:28:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] I kod djeteta od 15 godina,

872
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] ako jedna djevojčica

873
00:28:43,619 --> 00:28:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] zlostavlja drugu,

874
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo joj pomoći da vidi šta je ispod.

875
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,799
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da će biti neke sankcije,

876
00:28:49,799 --> 00:28:52,160
[SPEAKER_01] da mora shvatiti,

877
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:53,640
[SPEAKER_01] mislim sankcije u smislu ne kazne,

878
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:55,720
[SPEAKER_01] tako da možda sam pretjerano rekla,

879
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali ajmo joj,

880
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:58,460
[SPEAKER_01] ona se neće popraviti sa kaznom.

881
00:28:58,460 --> 00:29:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo joj pomoći da vidi zašto to radi.

882
00:29:01,779 --> 00:29:03,779
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno radi jer je ona nesretna,

883
00:29:03,779 --> 00:29:05,640
[SPEAKER_01] nesigurna i svašta nešto.

884
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, isto taj dječak ili djevojčica,

885
00:29:08,039 --> 00:29:11,980
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ako mu ti zrcališ ono što se u njemu događa,

886
00:29:11,980 --> 00:29:12,559
[SPEAKER_01] on onda vidi,

887
00:29:12,559 --> 00:29:14,140
[SPEAKER_01] aha, pa to ja imam,

888
00:29:14,140 --> 00:29:15,200
[SPEAKER_01] aha, to izgleda tako,

889
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,740
[SPEAKER_01] tako izgleda,

890
00:29:17,279 --> 00:29:18,819
[SPEAKER_01] da, pa to je to, to ja imam.

891
00:29:18,819 --> 00:29:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on sad uči što je uzbuđenje.

892
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] I ti si mu već time dala primjer,

893
00:29:23,579 --> 00:29:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] znači, granicu si postavila,

894
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] imenovala si emociju koja se dogodila

895
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:31,759
[SPEAKER_01] i pokazala si mu šta može

896
00:29:31,759 --> 00:29:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] i doslovno ćeš mu i reći,

897
00:29:32,859 --> 00:29:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] da, ako si uzbuđen možeš ovako

898
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] udarat, ne smiješ,

899
00:29:36,619 --> 00:29:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] ovako da, uzbuđen.

900
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,779
[SPEAKER_01] I ti si ga poučila što smije.

901
00:29:40,779 --> 00:29:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] I to je zapravo i taj proces što si prije pitala,

902
00:29:44,039 --> 00:29:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako nauči dijete da gleda

903
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] dublje u sebe, zapravo i da onda može

904
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:49,660
[SPEAKER_01] korigirati ponašanje svoje.

905
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da, uvijek mu dat kako može izrazit

906
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:54,259
[SPEAKER_01] to što ima,

907
00:29:54,259 --> 00:29:56,279
[SPEAKER_01] a izražava na neprihvatljiv način.

908
00:29:56,279 --> 00:29:58,339
[SPEAKER_01] Bez toga dijete ne uči

909
00:29:58,339 --> 00:29:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] kako treba.

910
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] što je s kaznama?

911
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Koje kazne su uopće prihvatljive,

912
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] jesu li ikakve?

913
00:30:06,579 --> 00:30:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] Čak sam dobila jedno pitanje,

914
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,660
[SPEAKER_00] je li ikad kazna,

915
00:30:10,660 --> 00:30:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali u smislu oduzimanje nekakvih

916
00:30:13,119 --> 00:30:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] povlastica potrebna u odgoju?

917
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo se prvo svojernuti na one,

918
00:30:17,220 --> 00:30:18,160
[SPEAKER_00] ja imam reći klasične,

919
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] tradicionalne kazne,

920
00:30:19,579 --> 00:30:21,220
[SPEAKER_00] opće da ne spominjem

921
00:30:21,220 --> 00:30:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] fizičko zostavljanje,

922
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,200
[SPEAKER_00] ali nažalost ima i toga,

923
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,779
[SPEAKER_00] pa se možemo malo dotaknuti toga,

924
00:30:25,779 --> 00:30:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali izoliranje,

925
00:30:28,099 --> 00:30:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] slanje u sobu,

926
00:30:29,099 --> 00:30:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da čak ima i po nekim vrtićima

927
00:30:31,180 --> 00:30:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] sučeva gdje se šalje djecu

928
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] u izolaciju i slično.

929
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:38,200
[SPEAKER_01] Kako to utječe na djecu?

930
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] Nije ti jedna kazna nije korisna

931
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:43,200
[SPEAKER_01] za djecu,

932
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] jer ona još uče.

933
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, neko ćeš dobro,

934
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali zamisli da nema kazna za odrasle,

935
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:48,599
[SPEAKER_01] tipa od policije kazne,

936
00:30:48,599 --> 00:30:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] za zatvori i slično.

937
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,700
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ok, mi moramo određene

938
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:53,380
[SPEAKER_01] velike mase odraslih ljudi

939
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:54,740
[SPEAKER_01] koji imaju odgovorno sami za sebe

940
00:30:54,740 --> 00:30:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] nekako kontrolirati da ovaj svijet funkcionira.

941
00:30:57,539 --> 00:30:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ali opet, ako ćemo sad pričati

942
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:00,759
[SPEAKER_01] o zatvorima, je dokazano,

943
00:31:00,759 --> 00:31:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam detalje,

944
00:31:01,980 --> 00:31:03,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali znam da je dokazano da zatvori

945
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] u kojima su se zatvorenici

946
00:31:06,019 --> 00:31:08,700
[SPEAKER_01] educirali i radili sa psihoterapeutima,

947
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:09,720
[SPEAKER_01] kad su izašli,

948
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] je manja stopa ponavljanja kriminala.

949
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,759
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, aha, opet govorimo

950
00:31:14,759 --> 00:31:15,640
[SPEAKER_01] o unutranjim svijetu.

951
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, kužim da tu, ok,

952
00:31:17,579 --> 00:31:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] trebaju postojati neke kazne

953
00:31:19,099 --> 00:31:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] za promet i slično i kriminal,

954
00:31:22,079 --> 00:31:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali djeca se tek razvijaju.

955
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] Imaju nas odrasle da im pomažemo,

956
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:28,559
[SPEAKER_01] da ih navigiramo,

957
00:31:28,559 --> 00:31:29,799
[SPEAKER_01] jer oni tek uče.

958
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, oni uče osjetiti

959
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] koja je to emocija ili potreba,

960
00:31:34,819 --> 00:31:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] zbog koje se ponaša na određen način,

961
00:31:36,799 --> 00:31:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] učini taj razmag i odabrat bolji put.

962
00:31:41,380 --> 00:31:43,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto kazne nemaju smisla?

963
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:45,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što kazne dokazano utječu

964
00:31:45,119 --> 00:31:47,319
[SPEAKER_01] na djetstvu sliku o sebi.

965
00:31:47,319 --> 00:31:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, jer djete stvara sliku o sebi

966
00:31:51,099 --> 00:31:54,160
[SPEAKER_01] onakvu kakvu mu ti zrcališ.

967
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako kad se on ponaša loše,

968
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,920
[SPEAKER_01] ti ga pošalješ u sobu,

969
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:01,279
[SPEAKER_01] znači ti si mu zrcalio takav

970
00:32:01,279 --> 00:32:02,740
[SPEAKER_01] ne želim da postojiš.

971
00:32:02,740 --> 00:32:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ignoriranje je zapravo

972
00:32:05,599 --> 00:32:08,779
[SPEAKER_01] pa jednaka kao i fizičko kažnjavanje.

973
00:32:08,779 --> 00:32:10,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, zatvaranje u sobu

974
00:32:10,059 --> 00:32:12,480
[SPEAKER_01] ili ignoriranje, sad ne pričam s tobom,

975
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] je poruka nemoj postojati.

976
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Neki su čak govorili

977
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] iz perspektive djece

978
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] koja je su kažnjavana,

979
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] da je bi im teže nekad padalo

980
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] ignoriranje i zanemarivanje

981
00:32:23,019 --> 00:32:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego udarati.

982
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,319
[SPEAKER_00] Jer tu dobijem bar neku pažnju.

983
00:32:25,319 --> 00:32:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je kontakt neki.

984
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] I kad pitaš da li ima korici,

985
00:32:29,079 --> 00:32:30,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam jednom ili dva put

986
00:32:30,779 --> 00:32:33,259
[SPEAKER_01] na story pitala odrasle osobe

987
00:32:33,259 --> 00:32:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje me prate.

988
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Što mislite o kazni koju ste dobivali?

989
00:32:37,579 --> 00:32:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je utjecala na vas

990
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:40,759
[SPEAKER_01] i šta mislite o tome?

991
00:32:40,759 --> 00:32:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, plakala sam dok sam čitala.

992
00:32:43,259 --> 00:32:44,700
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je danas,

993
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] uglavnom su to žene,

994
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] jer me prate uglavnom mame,

995
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:50,339
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je boli u tim ženama

996
00:32:50,339 --> 00:32:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] i kad su one meni pisale,

997
00:32:51,779 --> 00:32:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] kako su se osjećale,

998
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:54,200
[SPEAKER_01] to je horor.

999
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] Usamljeno, bezvrijedno,

1000
00:32:57,380 --> 00:33:00,240
[SPEAKER_01] konitko i ništa.

1001
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, samo sam se htjela osvetit.

1002
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] Razmišljala sam kako ću drugi put sakrit.

1003
00:33:07,099 --> 00:33:10,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nijedne nije pisala

1004
00:33:10,779 --> 00:33:13,160
[SPEAKER_01] to je to, naučila sam.

1005
00:33:13,259 --> 00:33:16,279
[SPEAKER_01] Iako ima ljudi koji će na ovaj podcast napisat,

1006
00:33:16,279 --> 00:33:18,700
[SPEAKER_01] tukli su me i treba da jesu,

1007
00:33:18,700 --> 00:33:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali ta osoba je toliko odustala od sebe

1008
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:22,140
[SPEAKER_01] da ona smatra da to zavrijeđuje.

1009
00:33:22,819 --> 00:33:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jedino kad generalno kažu što nama fali danas,

1010
00:33:25,539 --> 00:33:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] jer pogotovo malo generacije još starije od mene,

1011
00:33:29,079 --> 00:33:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] nas su tukli i što nam fali danas,

1012
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo generalno kao ok.

1013
00:33:33,319 --> 00:33:34,680
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali znaš zašto je to?

1014
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ismaš ok.

1015
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,700
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jer kad smo djeca,

1016
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] mi roditelje smatramo savršenima.

1017
00:33:40,079 --> 00:33:41,900
[SPEAKER_01] I kad nas roditelj kazni,

1018
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:43,220
[SPEAKER_01] mi ne mislimo da je on loš,

1019
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:45,480
[SPEAKER_01] nego uvijek ćemo misliti da smo mi loši.

1020
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:47,900
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako mislimo da je on loš,

1021
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] ko će nas čuvat?

1022
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] Mi trebamo tu figuru,

1023
00:33:51,119 --> 00:33:52,839
[SPEAKER_01] koja je idealna za nas.

1024
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] I teško je i danas razbiti tu iluziju

1025
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] da ti je nešto u djetinstvu nije bilo dobro.

1026
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] Djetinstvo je neki naš temelj,

1027
00:34:01,559 --> 00:34:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] ono da želiš sad to kopati još po tome

1028
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] da nešto nije bilo u redu,

1029
00:34:05,819 --> 00:34:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] da je nešto moglo bolje.

1030
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo imam osjećaj,

1031
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] znam, svjesna sam da i naši roditelji,

1032
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] moram reći,

1033
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] moji su stvarno radili po Montessorju,

1034
00:34:15,039 --> 00:34:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] a da nisu bili toga ni svjesni

1035
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] i blagoslovljena sam s time,

1036
00:34:18,099 --> 00:34:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam da je bilo roditelja koji

1037
00:34:20,099 --> 00:34:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] davali su sve,

1038
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali samo materialno,

1039
00:34:23,659 --> 00:34:25,139
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ti me misle davali smo sve.

1040
00:34:25,139 --> 00:34:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] I nekako su utkali u svoju djecu

1041
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve smo vam dali,

1042
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] sve smo vam dali,

1043
00:34:30,019 --> 00:34:31,679
[SPEAKER_00] možda makar nije bilo pažnje,

1044
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo bliskosti,

1045
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo masu toga,

1046
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali je mantra bila

1047
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:37,179
[SPEAKER_00] sve smo vam dali.

1048
00:34:37,179 --> 00:34:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je teško spoznat,

1049
00:34:39,079 --> 00:34:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] ok, niste mi baš sve dali

1050
00:34:40,619 --> 00:34:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] i priznati sebi

1051
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] i onda vučemo to kao

1052
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] sve nam,

1053
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] dobro nam je, ništa nam ne fali,

1054
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] ništa nam ne fali,

1055
00:34:46,539 --> 00:34:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] a zapravo ispod toga...

1056
00:34:48,019 --> 00:34:49,860
[SPEAKER_01] I onda ponavljamo to sa svojim djecom.

1057
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

1058
00:34:50,699 --> 00:34:52,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali dobro, i sa tim rojiteljima

1059
00:34:52,099 --> 00:34:53,860
[SPEAKER_01] netko nije bio s njihovim emocijama.

1060
00:34:53,860 --> 00:34:54,360
[SPEAKER_01] Emo.

1061
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:55,639
[SPEAKER_01] Naše emocije smo mi.

1062
00:34:55,639 --> 00:34:57,099
[SPEAKER_01] To je naša srž.

1063
00:34:57,099 --> 00:34:59,139
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, naš unutarnji svijet

1064
00:34:59,139 --> 00:35:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] su naše emocije.

1065
00:35:00,119 --> 00:35:01,639
[SPEAKER_01] I zapravo ako se ne bave

1066
00:35:01,639 --> 00:35:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] rojitelje emocijama,

1067
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,760
[SPEAKER_01] a uglavnom se odgoju ne bave,

1068
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] onda zapravo ne baviš se sa mnom.

1069
00:35:08,099 --> 00:35:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] Da, tako da,

1070
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] u konečnici

1071
00:35:11,639 --> 00:35:13,360
[SPEAKER_01] kazna ne dovodi.

1072
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, može,

1073
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] ako jako dobro kaznimo djete,

1074
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] ono hoće

1075
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne više dirati u čašu

1076
00:35:19,619 --> 00:35:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] ili zakasniti iz izlaska,

1077
00:35:21,099 --> 00:35:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali

1078
00:35:22,099 --> 00:35:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] to jedno kažnjeno djete

1079
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] će jako brzo početi vraćati.

1080
00:35:26,119 --> 00:35:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] Na primjer,

1081
00:35:26,619 --> 00:35:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] djete koje je

1082
00:35:28,179 --> 00:35:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] kažnjavano često

1083
00:35:30,079 --> 00:35:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] i odgajano na taj način,

1084
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,599
[SPEAKER_01] će sutra doć van

1085
00:35:33,599 --> 00:35:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] i zapući će marihuanu

1086
00:35:34,980 --> 00:35:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] samo zato

1087
00:35:36,039 --> 00:35:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] da ima svoje ja.

1088
00:35:38,099 --> 00:35:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] Jer si ga ti kažnjavao.

1089
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1090
00:35:41,079 --> 00:35:43,159
[SPEAKER_01] kužiš koliko daleko to ide.

1091
00:35:43,159 --> 00:35:44,820
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako danas ga kažnjavaš,

1092
00:35:44,820 --> 00:35:45,679
[SPEAKER_01] a šta ćeš sutra?

1093
00:35:45,679 --> 00:35:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sutra

1094
00:35:47,699 --> 00:35:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] imaš, ono,

1095
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,559
[SPEAKER_01] i rojitelji mi pišu,

1096
00:35:50,559 --> 00:35:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] on ima sad 15 godina,

1097
00:35:52,159 --> 00:35:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja fizički,

1098
00:35:52,559 --> 00:35:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] šta mu ja mogu s njim?

1099
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mu treba uzeti mobitel,

1100
00:35:56,699 --> 00:35:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet ne ide.

1101
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,059
[SPEAKER_01] On nađe drugi mobitel.

1102
00:35:59,059 --> 00:36:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] On ode opet van s društvom

1103
00:36:00,619 --> 00:36:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] i ti više nemaš kontrolu.

1104
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:03,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, stvar je

1105
00:36:03,699 --> 00:36:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] koliko si ti poštovanje

1106
00:36:06,099 --> 00:36:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] međusobno sagradio do tad.

1107
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:10,739
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja želim u životu

1108
00:36:10,739 --> 00:36:12,280
[SPEAKER_01] da me djete sluša

1109
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] jer me poštuje,

1110
00:36:13,260 --> 00:36:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] a ne zato

1111
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] jer me se boji.

1112
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

1113
00:36:16,559 --> 00:36:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kad izađe van,

1114
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] više me se ne boji.

1115
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam šta on radi.

1116
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da...

1117
00:36:20,820 --> 00:36:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, puno je toga toliko

1118
00:36:22,420 --> 00:36:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] zvuči lagano,

1119
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] a u praksi,

1120
00:36:25,539 --> 00:36:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

1121
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] još mi imamo malu djecu

1122
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] i djećemo kad dođu u pubertet,

1123
00:36:29,519 --> 00:36:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad se to gradi,

1124
00:36:31,139 --> 00:36:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] sad se gradi taj odnos.

1125
00:36:32,059 --> 00:36:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] A reci mi,

1126
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] da, znači kazne

1127
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] općenito ne.

1128
00:36:37,219 --> 00:36:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ispomenula si o oduzimanje privilegija.

1129
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] Eto.

1130
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto neka vrsta kazne?

1131
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:43,699
[SPEAKER_01] Je.

1132
00:36:43,699 --> 00:36:46,219
[SPEAKER_01] Samo što neki ljudi,

1133
00:36:46,219 --> 00:36:49,019
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam koliko su stručni u tome što rade,

1134
00:36:49,019 --> 00:36:51,179
[SPEAKER_01] je zagovaraju baš oduzimanje privilegija

1135
00:36:51,179 --> 00:36:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] i ja razumijem da je roditeljima to najlakše.

1136
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] To je najlakše.

1137
00:36:55,119 --> 00:36:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znači sve ovo svjesno što sam ti dan bez ekrana,

1138
00:36:57,739 --> 00:36:58,659
[SPEAKER_01] to spada tu kao.

1139
00:36:58,659 --> 00:37:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da, ili nemašeš na rođen da ne uzmem ti mobiteli slično,

1140
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:03,440
[SPEAKER_01] ali ponovno reakcija djeteta je ista.

1141
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači želiti se osveti, stvara lošu sliku o sebi,

1142
00:37:06,099 --> 00:37:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] samopuzdanje mu se spušta,

1143
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,679
[SPEAKER_01] sakriću drugi put ako i kako mogu,

1144
00:37:10,679 --> 00:37:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] znači jednostavno ne dobivamo ništa dobro.

1145
00:37:14,519 --> 00:37:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] Možda će paziti da drugi put ne napravi to isto,

1146
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] da kao mu opet ne uzmeš mobiteli će napraviti nešto drugo.

1147
00:37:20,619 --> 00:37:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] Znači opet nisi gradio njegove vještine

1148
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] koje mu trebaju za život.

1149
00:37:25,059 --> 00:37:28,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači mi u odgoju nismo tu da kažnjavamo

1150
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,519
[SPEAKER_01] za ponašnje koje nije okej,

1151
00:37:29,519 --> 00:37:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] nego da gradimo vještine za ponašnje koje je okej.

1152
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Uf, daj prvi to.

1153
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, kužim što želiš reći,

1154
00:37:34,639 --> 00:37:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali ajde malo.

1155
00:37:35,199 --> 00:37:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] Baš zvuči kao da je cijelo bogatstvo u toj rečenici.

1156
00:37:40,019 --> 00:37:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] I to je nekako ima osjećaj sve što sam do sad govorila.

1157
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] To je da, znači, kad ja...

1158
00:37:47,739 --> 00:37:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, koje alate, koji alati su onako primarni

1159
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] za jedno djete koje će jednog dana,

1160
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] pod tim mislim možda kad uđu pubertet,

1161
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] te neke kritične, formativne godine,

1162
00:37:59,639 --> 00:38:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] će ti se moći obratiti s povjerenjem,

1163
00:38:02,539 --> 00:38:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] neće se skrivat, neće bježati.

1164
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] Koje alate treba dati djetetu sad,

1165
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] dok ima 3, 4, 5, 6 godina?

1166
00:38:10,019 --> 00:38:12,019
[SPEAKER_01] Razvijat emocijonalnu inteligenciju.

1167
00:38:12,019 --> 00:38:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] A ona se razvija takvim pravilnim postavljanjem granica,

1168
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:18,780
[SPEAKER_01] uključit će emocije.

1169
00:38:18,780 --> 00:38:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači da postavimo granicu ponašanju,

1170
00:38:21,019 --> 00:38:24,780
[SPEAKER_01] imenujemo, aha, stvarno te zanimata čaša,

1171
00:38:24,780 --> 00:38:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] ili baš si ljut na seku.

1172
00:38:27,559 --> 00:38:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako je on udario sestru,

1173
00:38:30,019 --> 00:38:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] bez toga baš si ljut na sestru,

1174
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] da stvarno si ljut.

1175
00:38:33,739 --> 00:38:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] I razumijevanje, pa okej da bude ljut.

1176
00:38:36,039 --> 00:38:38,119
[SPEAKER_01] znači da dozvolimo emociju koju ima.

1177
00:38:38,119 --> 00:38:40,260
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kažnjavanjem ili stanjem u sobu,

1178
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:42,800
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo izignorirali njegovu emociju koja je okej,

1179
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] ljutnja je okej, ljutnja je borba za sebe.

1180
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:46,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, stvarno si ljut.

1181
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ne dozvoljavam da udaraš.

1182
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] Što možeš napraviti kad si ljut?

1183
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] I to je zapravo recept.

1184
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mama me vidi.

1185
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mama mi ne da da to radim.

1186
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:57,699
[SPEAKER_01] Mama je strogo rekla, to ne dozvoljavam.

1187
00:38:57,699 --> 00:38:59,719
[SPEAKER_01] Vidim da si ljut.

1188
00:38:59,719 --> 00:39:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, okej, sad ja i razumijem,

1189
00:39:01,119 --> 00:39:02,780
[SPEAKER_01] aha, pa da, udario sam sestru jer sam ljut.

1190
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, okej, aha.

1191
00:39:04,139 --> 00:39:05,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to radim kad se ljutim, okej.

1192
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mama mi ne da da to radi, znači to nije, okej.

1193
00:39:07,659 --> 00:39:08,760
[SPEAKER_01] Okej.

1194
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] I mama mi pokazuje što mogu.

1195
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mama je, pošto me nije odbila i kaznila,

1196
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] ona me već tim pristupom regulira.

1197
00:39:16,940 --> 00:39:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] Jer dijete ne može, regulacija znači stavljanje svog tijela u smireno stanje.

1198
00:39:22,599 --> 00:39:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kožiš, znači osjećam se okej.

1199
00:39:25,139 --> 00:39:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] I mama me već tim pristupom regulira

1200
00:39:28,599 --> 00:39:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] i kada tisuću milijon puta nadreguliramo svoje dijete,

1201
00:39:34,019 --> 00:39:36,780
[SPEAKER_01] ono onda razvije sposobnost regulacije samog sebe.

1202
00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] I onda, znači, pokažemo dijete tu što može napraviti kad je ljuto.

1203
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] Udariti ju ne smiješ.

1204
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš joj reći ovako, stop, ne želim da mi to radiš.

1205
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ili možeš joj reći, želim tu igračku.

1206
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ako si jako ljut, možeš ovako stisnuti ruke.

1207
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, dati mu primjere.

1208
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] I zapravo, to je proces koji mi njega učimo.

1209
00:39:54,559 --> 00:39:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, narušavamo njegov integritet.

1210
00:39:57,420 --> 00:40:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, odgajamo jedno dijete koji ima pozitivnu sliku o sebi.

1211
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] A takvi ljudi su bolji prema drugima.

1212
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ljudi koji rade drugima loše, ne osjećaju se dobro sami sa sobom.

1213
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:07,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je prvo.

1214
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo, razvija vještine emocijalne inteligencije.

1215
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, svjesno sebi, svojim emocijama, emocijama i potrebama drugih.

1216
00:40:14,719 --> 00:40:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što, ako sam ja u tom procesu koji sam opisala, svjesna emocija i potreba njega,

1217
00:40:21,019 --> 00:40:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] on već modeliranjem uči kako se to radi.

1218
00:40:24,699 --> 00:40:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] Onda će i on razumijet sutra više potrebe i emocije druge osobe.

1219
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:36,900
[SPEAKER_01] Onda u tom procesu uči regulirat sebe i kontrolirat sebe.

1220
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, zaustavit.

1221
00:40:38,039 --> 00:40:41,400
[SPEAKER_01] On mora prvo, dijete mora razumijet,

1222
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] on mora znati, imenovati i osjetiti svoju emociju da bi mogo se kontrolirat.

1223
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:49,139
[SPEAKER_01] Zato to oprosti što ovaj udara, nema smisla.

1224
00:40:49,139 --> 00:40:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da god on ne nauči zašto udara,

1225
00:40:52,119 --> 00:40:55,760
[SPEAKER_01] aha, uzbuđen sam, on se neće moći kontrolirat.

1226
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, osim ako ga udariš dobro, ali onda imaš posljedice neke druge.

1227
00:40:58,820 --> 00:40:59,900
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, problem na problem.

1228
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

1229
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, bolje zamijeniti samo datnu alternativu, ajde kad si uzbuđen,

1230
00:41:03,739 --> 00:41:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer ti dođu prijatelji i tako dalje, zagrli ih tipa ili tako nešto.

1231
00:41:07,420 --> 00:41:10,360
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali taj dio s emocijama mora biti,

1232
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] to se zove empatiško reflektiranje.

1233
00:41:12,659 --> 00:41:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Primijetili si da sam rekla, uzbuđen si.

1234
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram živjeti emociju koju moje djete ima.

1235
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je moje djete ljuto, da ljuci!

1236
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, moj ton se prilagođava ljutnji.

1237
00:41:23,559 --> 00:41:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] Moj ton, moje lice, moje tijelo,

1238
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer ono tako uči o svojim emocijama i o sebi.

1239
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:32,500
[SPEAKER_01] I tako uči prepoznat emocije drugih.

1240
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:35,860
[SPEAKER_01] I vidi da, aha, ok, to sad moji sestri sve to ok,

1241
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ovo mogla bi biti užena ljuta trara.

1242
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, zapravo ga mi opismenjavamo da je on u odnosima ok.

1243
00:41:42,059 --> 00:41:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] I da su sve emocije ok.

1244
00:41:44,159 --> 00:41:45,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, samo ne sve radnje.

1245
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:48,139
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, to je sav taj proces koji sad izgleda složan.

1246
00:41:48,139 --> 00:41:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, kroz edukaciju, stvarno idemo korak po korak

1247
00:41:50,739 --> 00:41:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] i slažu se te kocke.

1248
00:41:52,159 --> 00:41:53,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je to što sam ima bitla,

1249
00:41:53,820 --> 00:41:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] to je proces kojim naše djete onda postaje

1250
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] zrelije,

1251
00:41:57,559 --> 00:41:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] odgovornije,

1252
00:41:59,619 --> 00:42:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] bolje prema drugima,

1253
00:42:01,300 --> 00:42:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] poštuje više tebe,

1254
00:42:03,059 --> 00:42:05,099
[SPEAKER_01] empatičnije

1255
00:42:05,099 --> 00:42:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] i to što sam rekla

1256
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,360
[SPEAKER_01] dokazano je da djece koji imaju višu emocijonalni,

1257
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] da je emocijna inteligencija već je

1258
00:42:11,599 --> 00:42:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] prediktor uspjeha od logičke,

1259
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno od IQ-a,

1260
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] od kvazijenta inteligencije.

1261
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] A ono što, na što se mi svi

1262
00:42:20,019 --> 00:42:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] usmjeravamo je samo to da je

1263
00:42:21,619 --> 00:42:23,059
[SPEAKER_01] inteligentno, znanje,

1264
00:42:23,059 --> 00:42:24,639
[SPEAKER_01] ok, ali

1265
00:42:24,639 --> 00:42:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] najveći prediktor uspjeha je emocijonalna inteligencija

1266
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] i čak utječe i na fizičko zdravlje,

1267
00:42:30,539 --> 00:42:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] na sreću u životu,

1268
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] na akademski uspjeh,

1269
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] na karijeru,

1270
00:42:36,480 --> 00:42:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] znači ono, koliko je to važno.

1271
00:42:38,099 --> 00:42:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači moramo se time baviti u odgoju.

1272
00:42:40,199 --> 00:42:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1273
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, počeli smo se baviti time više.

1274
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] Baš sam htjela reći,

1275
00:42:44,460 --> 00:42:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] apropo ovog,

1276
00:42:45,099 --> 00:42:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo komentirali prethodne generacije,

1277
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] opet moram malo,

1278
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] malo im dati,

1279
00:42:51,619 --> 00:42:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako se to uopće na hrvatskom kaže,

1280
00:42:53,019 --> 00:42:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] milosti i prema tim starijim generacijama,

1281
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] to su opet neke generacije

1282
00:42:57,840 --> 00:43:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] koje nisu nekako nimale vremena

1283
00:43:00,460 --> 00:43:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] baviti se time,

1284
00:43:01,619 --> 00:43:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] jer su vrlo često više brnuli za egzistenciju.

1285
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, moćemo mi sad u ovoj blagodati,

1286
00:43:07,519 --> 00:43:09,719
[SPEAKER_00] možemo se više posjetiti tome.

1287
00:43:09,719 --> 00:43:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] Onda se opet nekad pitam,

1288
00:43:11,199 --> 00:43:13,679
[SPEAKER_00] možda sad idem previše u filozofiju,

1289
00:43:13,679 --> 00:43:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] ali je li onda ova današnja metoda,

1290
00:43:16,739 --> 00:43:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] svjesno roditeljstvo,

1291
00:43:17,920 --> 00:43:20,239
[SPEAKER_00] samo kritika na tradicionalni odgoj?

1292
00:43:20,239 --> 00:43:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] I što onda dolazi nakon toga?

1293
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] Što će biti kritika na svjesno roditeljstvo?

1294
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno, kakve krive drine će ispravljati naša djeca?

1295
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] Na svoje djece?

1296
00:43:31,500 --> 00:43:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mislim da će biti taj dio popustljivosti,

1297
00:43:34,659 --> 00:43:36,599
[SPEAKER_01] ako svjesno odlazi u popustljivo,

1298
00:43:36,599 --> 00:43:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne zna da je ipak roditelj taj koji vodi.

1299
00:43:39,179 --> 00:43:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je tanka granica između popustljivog

1300
00:43:45,079 --> 00:43:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] i roditeljstva gdje postoje jasne i čvrste granice

1301
00:43:47,539 --> 00:43:48,679
[SPEAKER_01] i jasna očekivanja.

1302
00:43:48,679 --> 00:43:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] Jer danas, ne znam,

1303
00:43:50,619 --> 00:43:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] ti sjedeš na tu stolicu,

1304
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] djete želi, oni se dižu.

1305
00:43:53,679 --> 00:43:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, jer eto, on želi baš tajtenjur,

1306
00:43:56,539 --> 00:43:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] baš tu stolicu, baš ovo, baš ono,

1307
00:43:58,239 --> 00:43:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] okej, želiš?

1308
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam sjela.

1309
00:44:01,099 --> 00:44:03,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, u redu je nekad,

1310
00:44:03,599 --> 00:44:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] evo, baš djete želi.

1311
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:07,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ono, ne mora sve biti kako djete želi.

1312
00:44:07,900 --> 00:44:09,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ja uvijek dam jedan primjer

1313
00:44:09,139 --> 00:44:12,519
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem sam osvjesla, jer vidim druge roditelje

1314
00:44:12,519 --> 00:44:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji se trude biti svjesni i sebe.

1315
00:44:15,800 --> 00:44:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] E sad primjer, bili smo kod prijateljice u dvorištu

1316
00:44:18,300 --> 00:44:19,260
[SPEAKER_01] i mi jedemo ručak.

1317
00:44:19,260 --> 00:44:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] I moja kćer je naravno pojela,

1318
00:44:21,139 --> 00:44:22,280
[SPEAKER_01] promrljala, okej,

1319
00:44:22,280 --> 00:44:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] znači pojela je koliko je htjela

1320
00:44:24,059 --> 00:44:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] i otišla je na ljuljačku.

1321
00:44:25,659 --> 00:44:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] I ja jedem, mama ljuljaj me, mama ljuljaj me.

1322
00:44:28,139 --> 00:44:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nisam dignula, ja jedem.

1323
00:44:30,079 --> 00:44:32,280
[SPEAKER_01] To je moja osobna granica.

1324
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ja trenutno jedem, ljubavi vidim,

1325
00:44:34,099 --> 00:44:35,659
[SPEAKER_01] jako biš voljala da te ljuljam.

1326
00:44:35,659 --> 00:44:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Kad pojedem, ću doć.

1327
00:44:37,579 --> 00:44:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] Većina roditelja, odmah,

1328
00:44:39,739 --> 00:44:41,440
[SPEAKER_01] jer oni moraju biti prisutni roditelji

1329
00:44:41,440 --> 00:44:43,460
[SPEAKER_01] koji što god djete zamisli,

1330
00:44:43,460 --> 00:44:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] tu sam ja.

1331
00:44:44,179 --> 00:44:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ili to ne znam,

1332
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,179
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam ni koliko je povezno,

1333
00:44:49,179 --> 00:44:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali došlo mi je na um,

1334
00:44:49,960 --> 00:44:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa ću reći da roditelji djece,

1335
00:44:52,119 --> 00:44:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] prijateljica mi ide, djevojčica njena

1336
00:44:54,300 --> 00:44:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] u prvi razred.

1337
00:44:54,980 --> 00:44:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] Kad dobio peticu, odmah idu kupi darove.

1338
00:44:57,960 --> 00:45:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] Molim, ono, darove,

1339
00:45:00,300 --> 00:45:02,059
[SPEAKER_01] jer si dobila pet.

1340
00:45:02,059 --> 00:45:04,440
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ono, ajmo predstav

1341
00:45:04,440 --> 00:45:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] da su nam se ponašati

1342
00:45:06,420 --> 00:45:07,639
[SPEAKER_01] kao da su nam djeca projekt.

1343
00:45:07,639 --> 00:45:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, pusti ga da ono uči radi sebe,

1344
00:45:10,599 --> 00:45:12,880
[SPEAKER_01] a ne da uči da bi dobilo dar.

1345
00:45:12,880 --> 00:45:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mislim da je u današnjem svijetu

1346
00:45:14,920 --> 00:45:18,579
[SPEAKER_01] udoljavanje od tog unutarnjeg

1347
00:45:18,579 --> 00:45:19,760
[SPEAKER_01] vlastitog vrednovanja,

1348
00:45:19,760 --> 00:45:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] unutarnjeg lokusa kontrola.

1349
00:45:21,739 --> 00:45:23,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti kupuješ dar, ti si kontrola.

1350
00:45:23,659 --> 00:45:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] I ne želim ja bi, ja učim svoje djete

1351
00:45:26,219 --> 00:45:28,440
[SPEAKER_01] da ono kontrolira sebe,

1352
00:45:28,440 --> 00:45:29,360
[SPEAKER_01] da ono vodi sebe.

1353
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja tu jesam vođa, da,

1354
00:45:30,539 --> 00:45:33,019
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne da ću ga, ono,

1355
00:45:33,019 --> 00:45:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] popuštat mu, kupovat mu nešto.

1356
00:45:35,179 --> 00:45:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ono, ajmo ga pustiti

1357
00:45:36,699 --> 00:45:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] da bude odgovorno

1358
00:45:37,739 --> 00:45:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] i da može vrednovat samo sebe,

1359
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] a ne da ono gleda mene ko Boga

1360
00:45:41,420 --> 00:45:43,340
[SPEAKER_01] i ono mora učit za pede

1361
00:45:43,340 --> 00:45:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] da bi dobilo dar

1362
00:45:44,559 --> 00:45:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] ili da ja ne bi vikala,

1363
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] ono, ne, unutarnju motivaciju

1364
00:45:48,400 --> 00:45:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] trebamo poticati.

1365
00:45:49,940 --> 00:45:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] To zvuči

1366
00:45:51,119 --> 00:45:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] kao jedan, onako,

1367
00:45:53,599 --> 00:45:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] idealni cilj

1368
00:45:54,599 --> 00:45:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] koji svimi roditelji želimo

1369
00:45:55,699 --> 00:45:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] dostići,

1370
00:45:56,920 --> 00:45:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je djete, ono,

1371
00:45:57,960 --> 00:45:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] samo pouzdano,

1372
00:45:59,900 --> 00:46:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] da ima to izgrađeno čvrsto,

1373
00:46:02,340 --> 00:46:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] ja,

1374
00:46:02,699 --> 00:46:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] evo, baš ću se sad

1375
00:46:04,500 --> 00:46:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] osunuti na jedno od pitanja,

1376
00:46:05,920 --> 00:46:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] makar se radi o malo starijem djetetu,

1377
00:46:07,619 --> 00:46:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] mama je napisala,

1378
00:46:08,539 --> 00:46:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] evo, pročitacu,

1379
00:46:10,659 --> 00:46:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] Han, valjda je povezano,

1380
00:46:13,280 --> 00:46:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je.

1381
00:46:13,840 --> 00:46:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjet će.

1382
00:46:14,639 --> 00:46:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se postaviti,

1383
00:46:16,260 --> 00:46:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] što reći curici

1384
00:46:17,139 --> 00:46:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] svojeg čeri,

1385
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali,

1386
00:46:19,099 --> 00:46:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] u ulazku u pubertet,

1387
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] kad ju najbolja prijateljica

1388
00:46:23,059 --> 00:46:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] od rođenja

1389
00:46:24,300 --> 00:46:25,139
[SPEAKER_00] ignorira

1390
00:46:25,139 --> 00:46:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] kad god dođe nekad treća.

1391
00:46:26,840 --> 00:46:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] Očito je ljubomora,

1392
00:46:28,119 --> 00:46:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] te prijateljice

1393
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] na određene uspjehe

1394
00:46:30,039 --> 00:46:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] prisutna,

1395
00:46:30,639 --> 00:46:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] ali uporno

1396
00:46:31,780 --> 00:46:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] povređuje svoju prijateljicu,

1397
00:46:33,300 --> 00:46:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] bilo o malovažavanjem,

1398
00:46:34,519 --> 00:46:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] glumatanjem,

1399
00:46:35,639 --> 00:46:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] uzdizanjem sebe,

1400
00:46:36,679 --> 00:46:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] što savjetovati,

1401
00:46:37,519 --> 00:46:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] inače smo i kućni prijatelji,

1402
00:46:40,659 --> 00:46:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] roditeljima,

1403
00:46:41,159 --> 00:46:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili kako pristupiti,

1404
00:46:43,079 --> 00:46:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] već je par puta,

1405
00:46:43,800 --> 00:46:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

1406
00:46:44,099 --> 00:46:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] plakala u takvim situacijama.

1407
00:46:46,159 --> 00:46:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kako napravi to

1408
00:46:47,739 --> 00:46:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] da ti djete dovoljno opet čvrsto,

1409
00:46:49,260 --> 00:46:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] da ga kao ne diraju

1410
00:46:50,159 --> 00:46:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] te vanjske stvari,

1411
00:46:51,059 --> 00:46:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] jel to ima veze s tim

1412
00:46:52,619 --> 00:46:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] samopouzdanu djete,

1413
00:46:54,920 --> 00:46:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] odnos s mama.

1414
00:46:56,280 --> 00:46:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, samo ovaj proces

1415
00:46:57,579 --> 00:46:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] koji sam ja tu ovako opisivala

1416
00:46:58,980 --> 00:46:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] s rukom,

1417
00:46:59,380 --> 00:47:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo gradi

1418
00:47:00,039 --> 00:47:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] samopouzdanu djete.

1419
00:47:01,079 --> 00:47:02,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, samo ovaj proces.

1420
00:47:02,739 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] A u ovoj situaciji

1421
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] konkretno je

1422
00:47:05,659 --> 00:47:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] složena je situacija.

1423
00:47:06,800 --> 00:47:07,880
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo je su kućni prijatelji,

1424
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] tako da svakako bi trebali

1425
00:47:09,880 --> 00:47:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] roditelje ovoj djevojčice

1426
00:47:11,039 --> 00:47:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] razgovarati s njom.

1427
00:47:11,960 --> 00:47:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] I tu bi ja postavila,

1428
00:47:13,659 --> 00:47:15,360
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo imali situaciju,

1429
00:47:15,360 --> 00:47:16,860
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je,

1430
00:47:16,860 --> 00:47:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] moja djevojčica je bila izbačena,

1431
00:47:20,460 --> 00:47:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači prvi dan su se igrale

1432
00:47:22,079 --> 00:47:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] ona i sestrična,

1433
00:47:22,940 --> 00:47:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] došla je treća djevojčica

1434
00:47:23,960 --> 00:47:25,360
[SPEAKER_01] na sanjikanju,

1435
00:47:25,360 --> 00:47:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] mi nismo to niskužili.

1436
00:47:26,840 --> 00:47:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nam je rekla

1437
00:47:28,179 --> 00:47:28,860
[SPEAKER_01] to tek kasnije

1438
00:47:28,860 --> 00:47:29,739
[SPEAKER_01] kad su svi otišli.

1439
00:47:29,739 --> 00:47:31,920
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad je došla

1440
00:47:31,920 --> 00:47:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] treća djevojčica,

1441
00:47:32,880 --> 00:47:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] su se ova od jučer

1442
00:47:34,199 --> 00:47:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] sestrična

1443
00:47:34,800 --> 00:47:35,980
[SPEAKER_01] i ta treća djevojčica

1444
00:47:35,980 --> 00:47:36,579
[SPEAKER_01] sanjikale.

1445
00:47:36,579 --> 00:47:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] I još poslije gledam,

1446
00:47:38,079 --> 00:47:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] pa da,

1447
00:47:38,440 --> 00:47:39,800
[SPEAKER_01] naša djevojčica se sanjikala

1448
00:47:39,800 --> 00:47:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] sa mnom

1449
00:47:40,400 --> 00:47:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] i sa tatom

1450
00:47:41,619 --> 00:47:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] cijelo vrijeme.

1451
00:47:42,099 --> 00:47:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] Uopće nisam išla za tim.

1452
00:47:43,619 --> 00:47:45,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je došla do njih,

1453
00:47:45,320 --> 00:47:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] čak,

1454
00:47:45,739 --> 00:47:47,079
[SPEAKER_01] što za introverta je

1455
00:47:47,079 --> 00:47:47,719
[SPEAKER_01] i za nju je

1456
00:47:47,719 --> 00:47:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] veliki uspjeh,

1457
00:47:49,199 --> 00:47:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] da je taj put došla do njih

1458
00:47:50,659 --> 00:47:50,800
[SPEAKER_01] i rekla,

1459
00:47:50,800 --> 00:47:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] ih tijela se sanjikat s njima

1460
00:47:53,119 --> 00:47:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] i jedna joj je rekla

1461
00:47:55,179 --> 00:47:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] šta nas pratiš.

1462
00:47:56,099 --> 00:47:57,659
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam,

1463
00:47:57,659 --> 00:47:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] ono što je bitno je

1464
00:47:58,900 --> 00:48:00,280
[SPEAKER_01] kao i za ovu djevojčicu

1465
00:48:00,280 --> 00:48:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] da su roditelji uz nju.

1466
00:48:01,340 --> 00:48:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1467
00:48:02,000 --> 00:48:04,780
[SPEAKER_01] da ne idemo odmah rješavati problem.

1468
00:48:04,780 --> 00:48:06,920
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi ne želimo djete,

1469
00:48:06,920 --> 00:48:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] to će se u životu događat.

1470
00:48:09,079 --> 00:48:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] Odbiće nas šef,

1471
00:48:10,699 --> 00:48:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] odbiće nas ovaj,

1472
00:48:11,699 --> 00:48:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] ona i svašta.

1473
00:48:12,960 --> 00:48:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] I mi zapravo jačamo djete

1474
00:48:15,199 --> 00:48:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] tako da gradimo

1475
00:48:16,980 --> 00:48:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] kapacitet nošenja s emocijama.

1476
00:48:18,960 --> 00:48:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] To se zove otpornost.

1477
00:48:20,739 --> 00:48:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] I to u djetinstvu radimo tako da,

1478
00:48:23,559 --> 00:48:24,579
[SPEAKER_01] na primjer,

1479
00:48:24,579 --> 00:48:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] prvo ne udovoljavamo.

1480
00:48:26,960 --> 00:48:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nego ako nešto ne želimo,

1481
00:48:28,300 --> 00:48:30,219
[SPEAKER_01] ako postavimo granicu u djetinstvu

1482
00:48:30,219 --> 00:48:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] i ono je nezadovoljno,

1483
00:48:31,199 --> 00:48:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] ja ga ne moram spašavati.

1484
00:48:32,400 --> 00:48:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1485
00:48:32,599 --> 00:48:34,280
[SPEAKER_01] moj djete može plakat pol sata,

1486
00:48:34,280 --> 00:48:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću samo reći,

1487
00:48:35,239 --> 00:48:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] tu sam.

1488
00:48:35,960 --> 00:48:36,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ono,

1489
00:48:36,360 --> 00:48:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] da,

1490
00:48:36,739 --> 00:48:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] teško ti je to.

1491
00:48:37,460 --> 00:48:37,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da,

1492
00:48:37,639 --> 00:48:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne dam ti da diraš ovu čašu.

1493
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znam,

1494
00:48:39,320 --> 00:48:40,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam uz tebe.

1495
00:48:40,099 --> 00:48:41,059
[SPEAKER_01] I time,

1496
00:48:41,059 --> 00:48:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja zapravo njemu pokazujem,

1497
00:48:42,099 --> 00:48:43,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad imaš tugu nije smak svijeta.

1498
00:48:44,400 --> 00:48:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] I time što je meni okej njegova tuga,

1499
00:48:46,539 --> 00:48:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] on zapravo gradi otpornost,

1500
00:48:48,199 --> 00:48:49,099
[SPEAKER_01] jer dobiva iskustva,

1501
00:48:49,099 --> 00:48:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] ha,

1502
00:48:49,280 --> 00:48:50,820
[SPEAKER_01] došla je emocija,

1503
00:48:50,820 --> 00:48:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] preplavila me,

1504
00:48:52,139 --> 00:48:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno ono,

1505
00:48:52,619 --> 00:48:53,599
[SPEAKER_01] prošla je kroz mene

1506
00:48:53,599 --> 00:48:54,320
[SPEAKER_01] i otišla je.

1507
00:48:54,320 --> 00:48:55,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam sad okej.

1508
00:48:55,320 --> 00:48:55,820
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1509
00:48:55,820 --> 00:48:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] uz prisutstvo roditelja zapravo ono doživljava to.

1510
00:48:58,099 --> 00:48:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako i za tu djevojčicu,

1511
00:48:59,920 --> 00:49:00,860
[SPEAKER_01] koja je već starija,

1512
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1513
00:49:01,079 --> 00:49:01,440
[SPEAKER_01] kažem,

1514
00:49:01,440 --> 00:49:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] ta sigurnost se od početka

1515
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] i otpornost razvija,

1516
00:49:04,480 --> 00:49:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali isto biti uz nju,

1517
00:49:05,519 --> 00:49:07,320
[SPEAKER_01] kako ti je to kad ti ona to radi?

1518
00:49:07,320 --> 00:49:08,280
[SPEAKER_01] Da,

1519
00:49:08,280 --> 00:49:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] i još ono,

1520
00:49:09,400 --> 00:49:10,320
[SPEAKER_01] želim sve čut.

1521
00:49:10,320 --> 00:49:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ti je?

1522
00:49:11,039 --> 00:49:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1523
00:49:11,199 --> 00:49:12,019
[SPEAKER_01] samo kako ti je?

1524
00:49:12,019 --> 00:49:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ne moramo riješiti.

1525
00:49:13,139 --> 00:49:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo prvo biti uz to,

1526
00:49:14,119 --> 00:49:15,639
[SPEAKER_01] pa to je baš teško.

1527
00:49:15,639 --> 00:49:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] I onda ispričati joj svoju priču.

1528
00:49:17,619 --> 00:49:17,780
[SPEAKER_01] Da,

1529
00:49:17,780 --> 00:49:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] znaš,

1530
00:49:18,159 --> 00:49:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] ja jednom kad sam bila u školi,

1531
00:49:21,039 --> 00:49:22,239
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da sam bila peti razred,

1532
00:49:22,239 --> 00:49:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] sad ja pričam svoju priču,

1533
00:49:23,440 --> 00:49:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] zvala sam prijateljicu

1534
00:49:26,659 --> 00:49:27,900
[SPEAKER_01] i rekla su da su kod jedne

1535
00:49:27,900 --> 00:49:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam došla u drugo selo

1536
00:49:29,239 --> 00:49:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] kod te prijateljice,

1537
00:49:30,340 --> 00:49:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] njih tamo nije bilo.

1538
00:49:31,340 --> 00:49:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su zapravo tišle na drugo mjesto.

1539
00:49:33,440 --> 00:49:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećala sam se najgore na svijetu.

1540
00:49:36,480 --> 00:49:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1541
00:49:37,079 --> 00:49:37,840
[SPEAKER_01] ali najgore.

1542
00:49:37,840 --> 00:49:39,239
[SPEAKER_01] I stvarno sam se osjećala najgore.

1543
00:49:39,239 --> 00:49:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] I tako je isto podijeliš sa svojom,

1544
00:49:43,019 --> 00:49:45,920
[SPEAKER_01] sa tim svojim djetetom.

1545
00:49:45,920 --> 00:49:49,219
[SPEAKER_01] I zapravo onda ono vidi da nije jedino u tome

1546
00:49:49,219 --> 00:49:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] i tu osjeća povezano s tobom

1547
00:49:50,760 --> 00:49:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] i lakše mu je.

1548
00:49:51,539 --> 00:49:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ide sljedeća,

1549
00:49:52,920 --> 00:49:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo ga učit vještinama nošenja sa time.

1550
00:49:55,840 --> 00:49:58,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, kako je to za tebe kad ona to radi?

1551
00:49:58,900 --> 00:50:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] Da li ti je ok pristajat na to?

1552
00:50:00,679 --> 00:50:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi ti njoj rekla?

1553
00:50:02,460 --> 00:50:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi ti napravila?

1554
00:50:04,460 --> 00:50:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo vidjeti možda i kako možemo to prevenirat.

1555
00:50:07,300 --> 00:50:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] Kada one dođu?

1556
00:50:08,900 --> 00:50:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ajmo sad da pomognemo svom djetetu

1557
00:50:12,760 --> 00:50:13,739
[SPEAKER_01] pronaći vještine.

1558
00:50:13,739 --> 00:50:16,119
[SPEAKER_01] Možda će to biti da jasno i glasno

1559
00:50:16,119 --> 00:50:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] i da vježbamo zajedno pred ogledalom

1560
00:50:17,599 --> 00:50:18,280
[SPEAKER_01] ili kroz igru.

1561
00:50:18,280 --> 00:50:20,679
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kroz igru pa jasno i glasno

1562
00:50:20,679 --> 00:50:21,840
[SPEAKER_01] vježbamo.

1563
00:50:21,840 --> 00:50:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, ona je sad došla

1564
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] i ne želim da se igraš samo s njom.

1565
00:50:25,179 --> 00:50:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] To meni nije ok.

1566
00:50:26,500 --> 00:50:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš li, sad ne znam koliko godina ima

1567
